Privacy Policy for Hair My Style

Last Updated: April 03, 2025

1. Introduction
Hair My Style is a free mobile application that provides hairstyle inspiration. We are committed to protecting your privacy and being transparent about our practices.

2. Information We Collect
The only information we may collect is:

Name (if voluntarily provided by you)

Photos/images (if voluntarily uploaded by you)

We do not collect, store, or process any other personal data. The app does not:

Track your location

Access your device information

Use cookies or analytics tools

Require any mandatory permissions

3. How We Use Your Information
Any name or photo you voluntarily provide is used solely:

To personalize your app experience

For the specific purpose you provided it (e.g., saving favorite styles)

4. Data Storage and Security

All data remains on your device unless you choose to share it

We implement reasonable security measures for any voluntarily shared information

You can delete your data at any time through the email below

5. Hairstyle Image Disclaimer
Our catalog includes images from public sources. We:

Do not claim ownership of these images

Assume no liability for their copyright status

Will remove any image upon request if infringement is found

6. Your Rights
You have the right to:

Use the app without providing any personal information

Request deletion of any data you've shared

Use the app freely within legal bounds

7. Changes to This Policy
We may update this policy occasionally. Any changes will be posted here.

8. Contact Us
For questions or copyright concerns:
Email: appmakingtutor@gmail.com
